# EventMatch — optional cloud backend (Supabase).
#
# The app works fully WITHOUT these (it falls back to localStorage). Fill them in to
# turn on real cross-device sync: profiles, connections and meeting requests.
#
# How to get them: create a free project at https://supabase.com → Project Settings →
# Data API / API Keys. Copy the Project URL and the *anon / publishable* key (NOT the
# service_role secret). Then run supabase/schema.sql in the SQL Editor. See BACKEND.md.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.local`) and fill in your values:

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
